title: See the Complete Balmain x H&M Collection
text:
View Slideshow
What with Kendall Jenner and Gigi Hadid's subway ads and Instagram's unexpected teaser , H&M's upcoming collection with Balmain has been hotly anticipated. The full look book is finally out today, with 38 photos of men and women decked out in gold embroidery, plus plenty of sparkly sequin dresses and Balmain T-shirts. Click through the slideshow for a complete preview of what you'll see in stores on November 5.
